  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title</strong></p>\n<p>Teacher &amp; Curriculum Writer</p>\n<p><strong>Occupation</strong></p>\n<p>PRIMARY and SECONDARY TUTOR</p>\n<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p>\n<p>Job Title</p>\n<p>Teacher and Curriculum Writer</p>\n<p>Occupation</p>\n<p>PRIMARY SCHOOL, SECONDERY SCHOOL TEACHER &amp; AEIS TEACHER</p>\n<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Science, Mathematics,Chinese and English Teacher</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Curriculum Writer</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You'll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Teach our regular online and offline classes</li>\n  <li>Record classes</li>\n  <li>Write and refine curriculum</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Teacher and Writer Requirem</strong></p>\n<p>Science,Math,Chinese and English-related</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Familiar with MOE Primary/ Secondary School Science syllabus</li>\n  <li>Experience in teaching children in primary school，</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office and Zoom</li>\n  <li>Successful candidates will be called down for a short interview</li>\n</ul>\n<p>· Flexible Work Arrangement</p>",
